ESMON is a Lustre performance monitoring tool.

For more documentation, please check:
    /doc

This monitoring tool depends on a specific version of Collectd with
Lustre plugins. It can be found at:
    https://github.com/DDNStorage/collectd

To build an ISO, do:
    1. Edit /etc/esmon_build.conf
    2. yum install python-dateutil PyYAML pandoc pandoc-pdf tetex-fonts texlive-xetex texlive texlive-* -y
    3. ./esmon_build

To run test, do:
    1. Build the ISO
    2. Edit /etc/esmon_test.conf 
    3. ./esmon_test

